[normal]Declaration of Interest[bold] by Key Forensic Services Ltd. Key Forensic Services Ltd is private UK owned company, offering a broad range of forensic services primarily to UK law enforcement agencies, and established as a direct competitor to the FSS. As such, Key Forensic Services is anticipating a more rapid uptake of FSS clients, which the company would otherwise have anticipated over a more protracted period via the scheduled Police procurement program.
